en_420749_0	Fifty nine Other Ranks who successfully completed the Counter Insurgency and Jungle Warfare (CIJW) Senior Non Commissioned Officers'/Non Commissioned Officers' Course No - 28 in the Army Training School at Maduruoya, passed out in a colorful ceremony on Saturday (19).
en_420749_1	The Commandant of the Army Training School Brigadier S.P.K.A Pilapitiya, graced the occasion as the Chief Guest.
en_420749_2	Award for the Best Student was received by Lance Corporal A. Waruna of 1 Commando Regiment.
en_420749_3	A parade coloured the event.
en_420749_4	Officers and Other Ranks took part in the day's arrangement.
